        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "A polished brass metronome ticks rhythmically within the haft of this *+1 striking gnome hooked hammer*. Gnome adherents of Brigh often attempt to reproduce this item as part of a ritual symbolizing methodical problem-solving and thoughtful craftsmanship.",
